Awesome 2025-01-20 08:07 a.m.
PAPERLESS ORDER

THIS CAUSE is before the Court upon the parties' submission of a Stipulation of Settlement, entered into by Clark Financial, LLC. and Xxprogamer123dash. The Court has reviewed the Settlement Agreement, and has determined that it is fair and reasonable and in the interests of the parties involved.

IT IS, THEREFORE, HEREBY:

ORDERED, ADJUDGED, AND DECREED that the Settlement Agreement is APPROVED, and the Court ADOPTS all terms as set forth therein; and IT IS FURTHER

ORDERED, ADJUDGED, AND DECREED that the Court retains and reserves jurisdiction to consider all further applications arising out of or in connection with the proposed Settlement; and IT IS FURTHER

ORDERED, ADJUDGED, AND DECREED that the above-captioned matter, upon completion of all terms stipulated therein, shall be STRICKEN from the active docket of the Court.

DONE AND ORDERED in Chambers at Mersea, Mayflower, on January 20, 2025.

/s/ AwesomePIays
Mayflower District Judge
